title: Mulayam Singh Yadav blesses Smriti Irani as she touches his feet in Parliament | WATCH - India Today
content: Mulayam Singh Yadav blesses Smriti Irani as she touches his feet in Parliament | WATCH  India Today
description: Samajwadi Party (SP) veteran Mulayam Singh Yadav was seen blessing Union Minister Smriti Irani as she touched his feet in Parliament on the first day of the Budget session on Monday.
